{
  "info": {
    "_postman_id": "f7c0a1e2-3b44-4f57-9a01-frutapp000001",
    "name": "FrutApp API",
    "description": "API del backend FrutApp (Ktor). Sprint 1: autenticación (JWT + refresh con rotación) y catálogo.\n\nVariables:\n- `baseUrl`: por defecto producción (https://frutapp-api.grandline.cl). Para local usar http://localhost:8080.\n- `accessToken` / `refreshToken`: se rellenan solos al ejecutar Registro/Login/Refresh (scripts en la pestaña Tests).\n\nFormato de error uniforme: `{ \"error\": \"<codigo>\", \"message\": \"<detalle>\" }`.",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "variable": [
    { "key": "baseUrl", "value": "https://frutapp-api.grandline.cl", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "accessToken", "value": "", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "refreshToken", "value": "", "type": "string" }
  ],
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "Health",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Health check",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/v1/health", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["v1", "health"] },
            "description": "Estado del backend. Responde 200 con status/version/timestamp."
          },
          "response": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Auth",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Registro",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "if (pm.response.code === 201) {",
                  "  const j = pm.response.json();",
                  "  pm.collectionVariables.set('accessToken', j.accessToken);",
                  "  pm.collectionVariables.set('refreshToken', j.refreshToken);",
                  "}"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"name\": \"Juan Pérez\",\n  \"email\": \"juan@ejemplo.cl\",\n  \"phone\": \"+56912345678\",\n  \"password\": \"abc123\"\n}"
            },
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/v1/auth/register", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["v1", "auth", "register"] },
            "description": "Crea una cuenta de cliente. Devuelve 201 con `user` + `accessToken` (JWT 15min) + `refreshToken`.\n\nValidaciones: email válido, contraseña mín. 6 caracteres con letras y números. Errores: 422 (validación), 409 (email ya existe)."
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Login",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "if (pm.response.code === 200) {",
                  "  const j = pm.response.json();",
                  "  pm.collectionVariables.set('accessToken', j.accessToken);",
                  "  pm.collectionVariables.set('refreshToken', j.refreshToken);",
                  "}"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"juan@ejemplo.cl\",\n  \"password\": \"abc123\"\n}"
            },
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/v1/auth/login", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["v1", "auth", "login"] },
            "description": "Inicia sesión. 200 con `user` + tokens. Credenciales incorrectas: 401."
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Refresh token",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "if (pm.response.code === 200) {",
                  "  const j = pm.response.json();",
                  "  pm.collectionVariables.set('accessToken', j.accessToken);",
                  "  pm.collectionVariables.set('refreshToken', j.refreshToken);",
                  "}"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"refreshToken\": \"{{refreshToken}}\"\n}"
            },
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/v1/auth/refresh", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["v1", "auth", "refresh"] },
            "description": "Renueva el par de tokens. ROTACIÓN: revoca el refresh presentado y emite uno nuevo. Reusar un refresh ya rotado o revocado: 401."
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Logout",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"refreshToken\": \"{{refreshToken}}\"\n}"
            },
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/v1/auth/logout", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["v1", "auth", "logout"] },
            "description": "Cierra sesión revocando el refresh token. Responde 204. El access token vivo expira solo en ≤15 min."
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Mi perfil (protegido)",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [{ "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{accessToken}}" }],
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/v1/auth/me", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["v1", "auth", "me"] },
            "description": "Datos del usuario autenticado. Requiere `Authorization: Bearer <accessToken>`. Sin token o token inválido/expirado: 401."
          },
          "response": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Catálogo",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Listar categorías",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/v1/categories", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["v1", "categories"] },
            "description": "Categorías ordenadas por `sortOrder`."
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Listar productos",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/v1/products?category=frutas&q=",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["v1", "products"],
              "query": [
                { "key": "category", "value": "frutas", "description": "slug de categoría (opcional): frutas | verduras" },
                { "key": "q", "value": "", "description": "búsqueda por nombre (opcional)" }
              ]
            },
            "description": "Productos activos. Filtros opcionales `category` (slug) y `q` (búsqueda por nombre). Cada producto trae `imageKey` que mapea al drawable de la app."
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Detalle de producto",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/v1/products/:id",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["v1", "products", ":id"],
              "variable": [{ "key": "id", "value": "", "description": "UUID del producto" }]
            },
            "description": "Producto por UUID. No existe: 404 con ApiError."
          },
          "response": []
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}
